      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, fluid properties, and operating conditions must match or bound the COU geometry and conditions within documented similarity arguments.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under blood-analog fluid conditions. Operating conditions span the COU envelope. Similarity analysis documented in validation plan VP-2022-01."
    },
