    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at Model Risk Level 2. The six remaining factors are appropriately scoped out or not assessed per ASME V&V 40 requirements for a Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under the defined COU. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 regulatory acceptance criterion across all five operating conditions.",
